{"tid":1097527,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恒指穿越三萬關收市 「四叔」李兆基會否再捐10億？","createTime":"2019-04-08T12:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T05:02:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5f626b7e0fac2c16d3ef8ec640378fc6945609e","tid":1097527,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"上月宣佈今年5月退休嘅恒地（012）創辦人「四叔」李兆基，早年喺個人自傳－－延續篇文末大發弘願，「恒生指數在三萬點時，每年捐獻港幣十億元；指數在四萬點時，每年捐獻港幣二十億元。」舊年恒指破3萬點，四叔已經陸續找數。不過，今日恒指首次喺年內破3萬點收市，究竟四叔要唔要再捐多10億，即係總共捐20億？<br />\n<br />\n首先華華要咬文嚼字先，恒指只要「在」3萬點時，每年已經要捐10億元，同埋記得係「每年」，即係今年恒指「在」3萬點時，要重新計過，所以應該要捐多10億元。<br />\n<br />\n華華問過恒地發言人四叔是咪又要再找數，不過今次口徑冇上次咁直接，可能兩年捐20億真係為數不少，發言人答案係：「建議記者可以喺5月28日（恒地股東大會）當日直接問四叔。」to捐or not to捐，that is the question。<br />\n<br />\n李華華<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190408/59464418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190408%2F59464418&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfpwi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=d04e9410\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190408%2F59464418&h=ac2a992a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190408/59464418</a>"},{"pid":"4533646650906f0cb1e80457f9341338de293796","tid":1097527,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"捐返落自己個基金"},{"pid":"42b3531e48cf565a688f84423adc1ac46d1fe305","tid":1097527,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"10億濕濕碎啦<br />\n對佢地黎講"},{"pid":"9fff8c51162c0307302ee9202de991f38b0aacab","tid":1097527,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"